{"tid":1448360,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［正式開戰］唔好再打遊撃快閃不合作 下次要直接還撃","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:51:18.000Z","uid":30205,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9242c1942e968833e3e7944b043c7e859e1ae3c5","tid":1448360,"uid":30205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:44.000Z","msg":"嬲到手都震撚埋<br />\n<br />\n今日開始 文宣 攬炒嗰啲麻煩繼續努力 依然好需要唔同渠道打撃呢個殺人政權<br />\n<br />\n但前線 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再主力遊撃堵路 依定人地唔當大家係人 想殺哂你地 或者打到你地殘廢呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鬼見一個打一個 畀人打一定要還撃 要佢地都感受死亡嘅恐懼</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">IF WE BURU, YOU BURN WITH US!!!!</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span>"},{"pid":"7579704b75a6da6b6ca12aff38cc4a116caefe48","tid":1448360,"uid":30205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"Dklm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9f6e2f74f7ef254541ccec77e32df5e50a6a35","tid":1448360,"uid":30205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:23.000Z","msg":"Dklm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fda952897848c57d3e571c973efde7bb68da86","tid":1448360,"uid":30205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"Dklm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1838c549b3681cdf92266dbd46db117a9642ce01","tid":1448360,"uid":30205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:45.000Z","msg":"Dklm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749d8e06b3b49470b15970e414